{"tid":652771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿嬌搵辣妹賀未婚夫生日","createTime":"2018-05-04T06:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T08:32:09.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8ab847cb9c2666eae09c786ce7ece8f2d36690","tid":652771,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"鍾欣潼（阿嬌）昨日在金鐘為英國時裝品牌Bora Aksu活動擔任嘉賓，獲贈兩幅肖像畫。阿嬌於本月25日到美國舉行婚前派對，她強調此行不是結婚：「我去參與就得，唔使搞咁多嘢，其實都唔知叫乜派對，總之係朋友聚會。」她笑言怕醜不會玩得太癲，雖然有朋友提議安排狂野男舞蹈員表演，但她覺得尷尬，更自嘲：「我未見過世面。」<br />\n未婚夫賴弘國於本月28日生日，阿嬌表示會安排火辣女舞蹈員作賀禮，她說：「我幫佢call定dancer，一定要靚，一定要好身材。」但明言接受不到辣妹埋身。兩人此行會順道影婚照，但目前未揀裙，打算各式各樣款都試一下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180504/20380329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F20380329&d=k8O58QSgpWBO%2F%2FiQWoKAonIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d158d0be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F20380329&h=1f362279\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180504/20380329</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180504/large/04ec2p6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180504%2Flarge%2F04ec2p6e.jpg&h=2c6f1969&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd37f4e5247e5d333ee4adfa150ae3be84a48acc","tid":652771,"uid":183302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:13:53.000Z","msg":"埋到單 立刻有番笑容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62638f25056f71ef4d09d6c06dfeb064c6c3fa1f","tid":652771,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾欣潼（阿嬌）昨日在金鐘為英國時裝品牌Bora Aksu活動擔任嘉賓，獲贈兩幅肖像畫。阿嬌於本月25日到美國舉行婚前派對，她強調此行不是結婚：「我去參與就得，唔使搞咁多嘢，其實都唔知叫乜派對，總之係朋友聚會。」她笑言怕醜不會玩得太癲，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然有朋友提議安排狂野男舞蹈員表演，但她覺得尷尬，更自嘲：「我未見過世面。」</span><br />\n未婚夫賴弘國於本月28日生日，阿嬌表示會安排火辣女舞蹈員作賀禮，她說：「我幫佢call定dancer，一定要靚，一定要好身材。」但明言接受不到辣妹埋身。兩人此行會順道影婚照，但目前未揀裙，打算各式各樣款都試一下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180504/20380329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F20380329&d=k8O58QSgpWBO%2F%2FiQWoKAonIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d158d0be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F20380329&h=1f362279\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180504/20380329</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180504/large/04ec2p6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180504%2Flarge%2F04ec2p6e.jpg&h=2c6f1969&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0275d4a23e95672adf78dbe7a17c1ab1784ed4","tid":652771,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"未見過世面？？？"},{"pid":"76ae947fb7e0f99728931b56338e5232acc070e6","tid":652771,"uid":92611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa0275d4a23e95672adf78dbe7a17c1ab1784ed4","tid":652771,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"未見過世面？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1e0da787493d272638c760ec33bf09f03998f3","tid":652771,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:29:09.000Z"